    BootReceiver

    This class is for the calendar page of the app.

    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.

    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).

    An activity that displays a Google map with a marker (pin) to indicate a particular location.

    Class to get location based on GPS

    Class to call all the connection neccessary to connect the app to php scripts to the database

    Class for registration page to sign up for the app
    MainMenu

    NotificationService
    Class to start the notification service and update every 15 seconds

    Page to input consent form details and update the database
    SubmitFeedback

    UploadFile

    User

    ViewFeedback

    ViewSpecificFeedback
    Class to view the specific feedback that the user clicked into from the list of all the feedbacks
